"title": "6512: salvation, necessity and basis of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6512: salvation, necessity and basis of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture stresses that fallen human beings are cut off from God on account of their sin. All need to be saved, if they are to enter into a new relationship with God as their Creator and Redeemer. Salvation is not the result of human achievement, privilege or wisdom, but depends totally upon the graciousness of a loving God, supremely expressed in the cross of Jesus Christ. People must respond in repentance and faith if they are to benefit from God's offer of salvation in Christ.</p>\n<h2>The necessity of salvation</h2>\n<h3>The universal rule of sin in human nature</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:6\">ISA 64:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:19-Rom3:23\">ROM 3:19–3:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:18\">ROM 5:12–5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:24\">ROM 7:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:3\">EPH 2:3</a></p>\n<h3>Sin cuts humanity off from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:2\">ISA 59:1–59:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22-Gen3:24\">GEN 3:22–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:1–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:18\">EPH 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>Sin enslaves humanity to evil</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:23\">JER 13:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:4\">HOS 5:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:11-Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:11–7:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:14-Rom7:20\">ROM 7:14–7:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:13-2Pet2:19\">2PE 2:13–2:19</a></p>\n<h2>Salvation is grounded in the love of God</h2>\n<h3>Salvation is not based on human achievement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:28\">ROM 3:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:7-Acts15:11\">ACT 15:7–15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:1-Rom4:3\">ROM 4:1–4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">ROM 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:16\">GAL 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:21\">GAL 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Salvation is grounded in God's love for his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:1-Deut7:8\">DEU 7:1–7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16-John3:17\">JHN 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16\">2TH 2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9-1John4:19\">1JN 4:9–4:19</a></p>\n<h3>Salvation is grounded in God's grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:22-Rom3:24\">ROM 3:22–3:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:16\">JHN 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:11\">ACT 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:15-Rom5:17\">ROM 5:15–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:1-2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:5-Eph1:8\">EPH 1:5–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:10\">EPH 2:4–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:14-1Tim1:15\">1TI 1:14–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11\">TIT 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:4–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9\">HEB 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Salvation and the work of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Salvation is grounded in the work of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30-Acts5:31\">ACT 5:30–5:31</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15\">1TI 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:42\">JHN 4:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10-Acts4:12\">ACT 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:9-Rom5:10\">ROM 5:9–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20-Phil3:21\">PHP 3:20–3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9-2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:5–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:24-Heb7:25\">HEB 7:24–7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:14\">1JN 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's death was totally sufficient for salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:1-John17:4\">JHN 17:1–17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10-Acts4:12\">ACT 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:3-Gal1:4\">GAL 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:5-Eph1:10\">EPH 1:5–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5-1Tim2:6\">1TI 2:5–2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9-2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10\">HEB 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9-1John4:10\">1JN 4:9–4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:10\">REV 7:9–7:10</a></p>\n<h2>Salvation demands a human decision</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:50\">LUK 8:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:17-John3:18\">JHN 3:17–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:37-Acts2:39\">ACT 2:37–2:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:25\">HEB 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:4–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:10\">1JN 5:10</a></p>",
